{"tid":1848493,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"口罩不趕快援助中國 馬英九批「沒氣度」「沒人性」","createTime":"2020-01-28T13:16:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T16:50:37.000Z","uid":49643,"like":9,"dislike":52,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"850ded1b64f0aabdeddbbe119617586215423aa9","tid":1848493,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:16:10.000Z","msg":"2020-01-28 16:31:10<br />\n〔記者許麗娟／高雄報導〕前總統馬英九春節發送祈福卡的行程滿檔，今天下午至高雄褒忠義民廟、鳳山天公廟、大寮慈后宮3個行程，面對媒體詢問罷韓團體今赴中選會領表啟動二階罷韓，馬英九回應「沒有什麼看法」，倒是對政府口罩禁出口再表意見，馬英九批全世界都在援助，若再不做以後回頭來看會發現「政府實在沒有人性」。<br />\n<br />\n對於副總統當選人賴清德認為武漢肺炎疫情越來越嚴重，正是中國與台灣共同合作的時機，馬英九表示，他覺得賴清德的主張是正確的，「台灣現在的口罩應該還有能力捐給大陸（中國），尤其是全世界都在捐，如果我們不捐，不但顯示我們氣度不夠，這表示我們對國際事務很陌生，人道的援助不應該去考慮政治，我們政府應該趕快運送口罩到大陸（中國）。」<br />\n<br />\n馬英九指出，實際上從年初二開始，台灣口罩的製造商已經開始在生產了，大概1天可以生產1百多萬個，對台灣來講應該是夠用的，「如果我們再不做的話，以後回頭來看，發現政府實在是沒有人性，我覺得這是不好的標幟，全世界都在援助的時候，結果我們同文同種的中國人反而不做，這是非常失策、也是非常沒有愛心的做法。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3051038?fbclid=IwAR0GWkTLuYsAjdmpgVwtHGuVz-Bs42eylh-KhRiOBNNYSzSA8cj2BuS_hC4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3051038%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0GWkTLuYsAjdmpgVwtHGuVz-Bs42eylh-KhRiOBNNYSzSA8cj2BuS_hC4&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGZ2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=17ae8674\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3051038%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0GWkTLuYsAjdmpgVwtHGuVz-Bs42eylh-KhRiOBNNYSzSA8cj2BuS_hC4&h=f6b2fbb3\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3051038?fbclid=IwAR0GWkTLuYsAjdmpgVwtHGuVz-Bs42eylh-KhRiOBNNYSzSA8cj2BuS_hC4</a><br />\n依條仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae6af715a51a587745ce33be5633129c0f707dc1","tid":1848493,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:16:27.000Z","msg":"入去推10下！<br />\n<br />\n「正視聽！」拆解林鄭記招政策幾乎零作用！全力籌備1.29 2.03大三罷！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1848456\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1848456</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a97ce0dd3d19eb1756be0e70c381836f2f749dda","tid":1848493,"uid":38904,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:17:42.000Z","msg":"非洲人冇錢使又唔見你捐返啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fc11257c476f01d260cc847600e64211526147d","tid":1848493,"uid":35378,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:18:00.000Z","msg":"佢咁有氣度咁有人性咪自己出錢囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74ecaa63f5fca872374595fb0e74793aae1a10d3","tid":1848493,"uid":3747,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:18:07.000Z","msg":"用中華民國總統蔡英文名義捐<br />\n睇下武漢收唔收"},{"pid":"f0e6b34454f2dd0bfa676f993ff7b2ba7328f619","tid":1848493,"uid":165361,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:18:37.000Z","msg":"你咁有人性,咪用國民黨D 錢買口罩捐過去"},{"pid":"a26c2ef9bd81430ebe59842c7459d5f5b1a2116b","tid":1848493,"uid":73381,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:18:40.000Z","msg":"依家全台灣都買唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1f256b74a70a70afd96811a8ab56ff3430510ea","tid":1848493,"uid":77196,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:18:59.000Z","msg":"唔餵飽自己仔女而將碗飯拎去俾街外人咪仲冇人性<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc93735a20d753fe5598d0dbfa929fcecea50770","tid":1848493,"uid":190383,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:20:01.000Z","msg":"一日一百萬個 香港都唔夠用啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n定佢一個口罩用幾日？"},{"pid":"512d8b9992063060e5a7ce379f8d5f58c685bf81","tid":1848493,"uid":311128,"like":0,"dislike"